Product Description: Cauliflower Pilaf with Fresh Turmeric and Fennel, New Seasons Kitchen Collective Meal Kits, Net wt. 2 lb 4 oz (1007 gr), UPC 840600109563.     The ingredients statement of the finished product package is labeled in parts: ***INGREDIENTS:  Cauliflower, Water, Fennel, Onion, Lemon Juice, Golden Raisins, Fresh Turmeric Root, Cilantro, Blanched Almonds, Fresh Mint Leaves, Garlic, Paprika, Dill Weed, Vegetable Base (vegetable juices {tomato, mushroom, onion, carrot, celery, sunflower oil}, yeast extract, salt), Cinnamon, Cloves, ***Contains: Tree Nuts (almonds)***".    The clear container of almond  inside the meal kit was mis-labeled as "Peanut".
Reason for Recall: Cauliflower Pilaf meal kit is recalled because the Almonds container, packaged in a separate clear containers inside the kit, was mislabeled with a sticker that declares peanut.
